        <h2>
		<img border="0" src="images/badge/nsxfacilitator.jpg" width="200" height="200" align="right">Facilitators 
		provide services to issuers</h2>
		<p>Facilitators are groups of firms that can provide listing services, 
        in various, capacities to companies seeking a listing. </p>
        <p>The NSX does not warrant the&nbsp; services of facilitators but does 
        require facilitators to undergo a registration process so that only 
        firms of high integrity are recognised facilitators. When contacting 
        facilitators please include sufficient detail about the entity to list 
        and also allow sufficient time for a considered response to your 
        request. </p>
		<h2>How to register as a facilitator</h2>
        <p>For more information about facilitators please refer to the 
        <a href="facilitator_apply.asp">facilitator registration page</a>.</p>
